OL,3,CPlans published to redraw political
OL,4,Cmap of Wales ahead of MS increase
OL,6,FPlans have been published to redraw
OL,7,Fconstituencies ahead of the next
OL,8,FSenedd elections in 2026.
OL,10,FThe changes follow the decision to
OL,11,Fincrease the number of politicians in
OL,12,Fthe Welsh Parliament to 96 at the next
OL,13,Felection, up from the current 66.
OL,15,FThe new proposed political map of
OL,16,FWales will split the country into 16
OL,17,Fconstituencies, a reduction, and each
OL,18,Fconstituency will have six elected
OL,19,Fmembers.
