OL,4,Cmap of Wales ahead of MS increase
OL,6,FThe plans encompass the 32 UK
OL,7,FParliament constituencies revised
OL,8,Fbefore the 2024 General Election.
OL,10,FThe proposals, drawn up by the
OL,11,FBoundary Commission for Wales, are now
OL,12,Fopen for public consultation, and the
OL,13,Fcommissioners behind the plans are
OL,14,Fseeking public feedback.
