OL,3,CPlans published to redraw political
OL,4,Cmap of Wales ahead of MS increase
OL,6,FChanges to the number of Members of
OL,7,Fthe Senedd (MS) were proposed as part
OL,8,Fof the Welsh Government's cooperation
OL,9,Fagreement with Plaid Cymru. They argue
OL,10,Fthat as the powers of the Senedd have
OL,11,Fgrown since devolution, so too has the
OL,12,Fworkload on politicians.
OL,14,FThey believe for the Welsh Parliament
OL,15,Fto continue to function there needs to
OL,16,Fbe more representatives in Y Siambr
OL,17,F(the chamber).
