OL,3,CPlans published to redraw political
OL,4,Cmap of Wales ahead of MS increase
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru Leader Rhun ap Iorwerth MS
OL,7,Fsaid the bill paved the way for a
OL,8,Fparliament "fit for the 21st century"
OL,9,Fand provided a new foundation to build
OL,10,Fa fairer Wales and to prepare for
OL,11,Fpolitical and constitutional change.
OL,13,FHowever, the increase in Senedd
OL,14,Fmembers has been criticised by
OL,15,Fopposition politicians in the Welsh
OL,16,Fparliament.
OL,18,FAndrew RT Davies MS, Leader of the
OL,19,FWelsh Conservatives, has referred to
OL,20,Fthe changes as "a national
OL,21,Fembarrassment".
